{"tid":1891702,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實前港督彭定康已經解答左警方對《頭條新聞》批評","createTime":"2020-02-22T04:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:47:37.000Z","uid":320828,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b77d140175fd149eac1b06ff6bbe28a513505cee","tid":1891702,"uid":320828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"《頭條新聞》應該叫警慌睇翻段片，彭定康解答左<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8aT8Kw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8aT8Kw.png&h=4c5a7f1e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YP8uG4z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYP8uG4z.png&h=078f017e&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BVnutukfWkk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBVnutukfWkk&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=f31794f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BVnutukfWkk</a><br />\n&quot;HK is a very special place. I was happier when I was in HK than ever been another time in my life. &quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Sometimes people make fun in any way which would be a bit hurtful, but nevertheless if you believe in a free society, you accepted the part of the nature of political weather. As a politician, you're better of being made fun of than not notice at all. &quot;<br />\n有時嘲笑的手法會令人感到不快，但是，若抱持自由的信念，便得接受這是政治氣候的本質之一。身為政治人物，被人嘲弄總勝過無人理會。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;My anxiety is this: not that this community's autonomy would be usurped by Peking, but that it could be given away bit by bit by some people in Hong Kong.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n                                                                                            -- Christopher Pattern<br />\n我感到憂慮，不是因爲香港的自主權會被北京剝奪，而是它將逐點斷送在香港某些人手裏。"},{"pid":"88d5e35af5176a60565c534a77628115f48590ca","tid":1891702,"uid":103617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"譯得好好"},{"pi